Brighton Tide is a script to scrape the tide time information
from VisitBrighton.com and post them to Twitter.

http://richard.dallaway.com/still-loving-the-scala

RUNNING THE APP

$ sbt run

RUNNING THE SPECS TESTS

$ sbt test


History:

Prior to 3 Jan 2011, the VisitBrightonScraper was used for tide data.  Unfortunately, each January the web site contained no data for a few days, which is inconvenient.

